PetroChina Seeks Oil Storage Space in U.A.E., Reuters Says

-- B y   A n t h o n y   D i P a o l a
-- 
2011-03-21T17:55:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-21/petrochina-seeks-oil-storage-space-in-u-a-e-reuters-says.html
PetroChina Co. may be seeking as
much as 1 million cubic meters of storage capacity for refined
oil products at the United Arab Emirates port of Fujairah,
 Reuters  reported without saying where it got the information.  The company, a unit of China National Petroleum Corp., is
in talks with the government of Fujairah about potential
building storage capacity, the news agency reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anthony DiPaola in Dubai at 
 adipaola@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:  Stephen Voss  on   sev@bloomberg.net . 